</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="AE1B4140E86455150C35A4AA565E10E6" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="A69BF93C05FF1833CCA81E296B885C59" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">Distribution and habitats.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A7DA3818C15E633A566B3FD344743C38" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">
<taxonomicName id="E919CFCC9D85B83B4AB00709DCF8E718" authority="subsp. acuminata" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hydrangeaceae" genus="Hydrangea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hydrangea acuminata subsp. acuminata" order="Cornales" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="acuminata" subSpecies="acuminata">Hydrangea acuminata subsp. acuminata</taxonomicName>
is widely distributed on the main island of Kyushu, and usually grows on the soil near streams and often on cliffs, and sometimes in disturbed habitats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F3815CA5DB0937AA31C2AFA6054AF80C" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" type="notes">
<paragraph id="E6ADE17D7FD05E7A49C6A48A21450FBB" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4DB309AB221CF4A94CA64037FEC0E74C" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">
<bibRefCitation id="4F7CD652D71BD66864FAF8856E3A0DB3" author="Ohba, H" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Japanese Botany" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" pagination="345 - 350" publicationUrl="http://www.jjbotany.com/pdf/JJB_091_345_350.pdf" refId="B19" refString="Ohba, H, Akiyama, S, 2016. Generic segregation of some sections and subsections of the genus Hydrangea (Hydrangeaceae). Journal of Japanese Botany 91 (6): 345 - 350, http://www.jjbotany.com/pdf/JJB_091_345_350.pdf" title="Generic segregation of some sections and subsections of the genus Hydrangea (Hydrangeaceae)." url="http://www.jjbotany.com/pdf/JJB_091_345_350.pdf" volume="91" year="2016">Ohba and Akiyama (2016)</bibRefCitation>
treated this species as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="2826F0EBD4025EA76D33C2DC25D96B89" class="Insecta" family="Hydrangeaceae" genus="Hortensia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hortensia serrata" order="Cornales" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serrata">
<emphasis id="0DD201F8C6C741F498E68A476F2E190A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">Hortensia serrata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, our phylogenetic analysis described below supports the treatment of it as a distinct species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
